  "title": "Log Stubs",
  "description": "Gives logs a chance of spawning with a stub on one of the sides of it.",
  "body": "![About](https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/cached_images/19d332cdab77737cd016fd7c1ae13efef260cbc7_0.webp)\n\n**Log Stubs** gives all wood types a chance to have a stub attached to their model. Stubs can appear on any side except the top or bottom of the log. They do not appear when the log is stripped or when it is crafted into the “wood” variant.\n\nIn the blockstates, each stub variant has a weight of 1, and the regular log model has a weight of 80.",
